token_lists.title: Grande Dame on tour
token_lists.description:
"Grande Dame" Special edition collection.
Each artwork is generated with code of the "Grande Dame" project on FxHash.
The code is adapted for each iteration to create curated pieces inspired by cities around the world.

Project inspired by the artworks of Vera Molnár ('Grande Dame' of digital art), one of the first women artists to use computers in her practice.

token_lists.title: Another Photography board / curated by Kika Nicolela
token_lists.description: Photography was my first passion. So here goes a selection of my personal favorites in Versum.

token_lists.title: Secrets of this Night
token_lists.description:
Let our Ukrainian nights be like in these photos, without explosions, without fear. Let beautiful naked girls meet on our dear ones, and not military tanks and permits. I am for world peace. Slava Ukraine! 

50% of the income from the sales of this NFT collection goes to support the Ukrainian army and help Ukrainian refugees affected by the consequences of the war in Ukraine. 

All girls were 18 or older at the time of shooting.

token_lists.title: Pylons & Pennants
token_lists.description: Witches, Warriors, some Shepherds and their signs. A body of work ranging in materials from drawing and painting to installation and sculpture.

token_lists.title: Not A Number
token_lists.description: She is not a number. She is a precision bitwise operator.

token_lists.title: "AI Invasion!" Neural / AI Art NFTs
token_lists.description:
Stuff made with tools like CLIP/VQGAN, Disco Diffusion, Phosphor etc., and, more recently, AI text prompts.

Most is appealing, but apparently MUCH too easy to generate (sic!). It is very hard to tear the average from the great, so please be patient as this board evolves...

token_lists.description: Collaboration project about sharing our ideas of Beauty.
